Name: Psyche_Parameters
Description: Class for Psyche related values.

Name: mission_phase_name
Description: The Psyche Mission phase name.

Name: approach
Description: The Psyche mission phase used for the approach to 16 Psyche, last 100 days.

Name: atlo
Description: The Psyche mission phase used for ATLO.

Name: cruise_1
Description: The Psyche mission phase used for the cruise 1 period, lasting 26 months.

Name: cruise_2
Description: The Psyche mission phase used for the cruise 2 period, lasting 36 months.

Name: ico
Description: The Psyche mission phase used for the initial checkout (ICO), lasting 100 days.

Name: launch
Description: The Psyche mission phase used for spacecraft launch.

Name: mga
Description: The Psyche mission phase used for the Mars gravity assist, lasting 62 days.

Name: orbit_a
Description: The Psyche mission phase used for orbit A operations, lasting 56 days.

Name: orbit_b1
Description: The Psyche mission phase used for orbit B1 operations, lasting 92 days.

Name: orbit_b2
Description: The Psyche mission phase used for orbit B2 operations, lasting 100 days.

Name: orbit_c
Description: The Psyche mission phase used for orbit C operations, lasting 100 days.

Name: orbit_d
Description: The Psyche mission phase used for orbit D operations, lasting 100 days.

Name: orbit_transfer_a_to_b1
Description: The Psyche mission phase used for orbit transfer A-to-B1, lasting 17 days.

Name: orbit_transfer_b1_to_d
Description: The Psyche mission phase used for orbit transfer B1-to-D, lasting 98 days.

Name: orbit_transfer_c_to_b2
Description: The Psyche mission phase used for orbit transfer C-to-B2, lasting 23 days.

Name: orbit_transfer_d_to_c
Description: The Psyche mission phase used for orbit transfer D-to-C, lasting 90 days.

Name: orbital_operations
Description: The Psyche mission phase used for the entire orbital operations period, lasting 26 months.

Name: preflight
Description: The Psyche mission phase usef for preflight operations.

Name: test
Description: The Psyche mission phase used for general testing purposes.

Name: orbit_number
Description: This value denotes the orbit number during orbital operations.

Name: release_number
Description: This value denotes the release number when a product was published.

Name: spacecraft_clock_start
Description: This value denotes the observation spacecraft clock start (SCLK) recorded.

Name: spacecraft_clock_stop
Description: This value denotes the observation spacecraft clock stop (SCLK) recorded.

Name: spacecraft_clock_start_corrected
Description: This value denotes the observation spacecraft clock start (SCLK) recorded, corrected for any clock updates.

Name: spacecraft_clock_stop_corrected
Description: This value denotes the observation spacecraft clock stop (SCLK) recorded, corrected for an clock updates.

Name: spacecraft_clock_partition
Description: This value denotes the spacecraft clock partition, tracking any clock resets.

Name: spacecraft_fsw_dictionary_version
Description: This value denotes the version of the spacecraft fsw dictionary in use.
Version 5.4.2.1 of the Psyche FSW dictionary.
Version 5.4.2.2 of the Psyche FSW dictionary.

Name: spacecraft_active_flight_computer
Description: This value denotes the spacecraft pce active and in use.

Name: A
Description: The Psyche spacecraft active pce A.

Name: B
Description: The Psyche spacecraft active pce B.
